 to reduce time and costs in drug R&D.\nIndian firms shift focus from generics, boosting global revenue with new drug discoveries.","summary":"Sun Pharma explores AI to reduce time and costs in drug R&D.\nIndian firms shift focus from generics, boosting global revenue with new drug discoveries.","url":"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/healthcare/biotech/pharmaceuticals/indian-pharma-may-take-ai-pill-to-cut-time-and-costs-in-drug-rd/articleshow/128435573.cms","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-17T00:00:00","source":"The Economic Times"},{"id":"479243","title":"Sun Pharma executed a block trade worth Rs. 56.4 crores for ~330,164 shares.\nThe transaction was priced at Rs. 1708.2 per share.","summary":"Sun Pharma executed a block trade worth Rs. 56.4 crores for ~330,164 shares.\nThe transaction was priced at Rs. 1708.2 per share.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T12:20:53","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"260209150150457","title":"Sun Pharma, Dr Reddy's, and Lupin stress boosting drug innovation.\nPromoters see potential for India to become a pharma innovation hub.","summary":"Sun Pharma, Dr Reddy's, and Lupin stress boosting drug innovation.\nPromoters see potential for India to become a pharma innovation hub.","url":"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/healthcare/biotech/pharmaceuticals/sun-pharma-dr-reddys-lupin-call-for-big-push-in-drug-innovation/articleshow/128114781.cms","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T00:00:00","source":"The Economic Times"},{"id":"260208149596246","title":"US market continued to impact Indian pharma in Q3FY26 due to pricing pressure.\nCompanies launched complex therapies to counter competition and product challenges.","summary":"US market continued to impact Indian pharma in Q3FY26 due to pricing pressure.\nCompanies launched complex therapies to counter competition and product challenges.","url":"https://www.business-standard.com/industry/news/us-market-drag-indian-pharma-q3fy26-pricing-pressure-competit